---
import Hero from "../../../components/hero/Hero.astro";
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";

import styles from "./mission.module.scss";

const contentArray = [
	{
		heading: "Quality Living, Value for Money",
		text: "Mangaly Group is committed to delivering high-quality residential spaces that provide true value for money. Every project is designed with careful planning and attention to detail, ensuring long-term satisfaction for homeowners. Our developments offer a balance of affordability, premium amenities, and enduring value, making homeownership a rewarding investment.",
		image: "/mission-1.svg",
	},
	{
		heading: "Sustainable and Green Living",
		text: "We believe in building a future that aligns with environmental responsibility. Our projects incorporate sustainable construction practices, energy-efficient designs, and green spaces to promote a healthier and eco-friendly lifestyle. By focusing on sustainability, Mangaly Group contributes to a greener and cleaner India.",
		image: "/mission-2.svg",
	},
	{
		heading: "Building Communities for Tomorrow",
		text: "Beyond constructing homes, Mangaly Group aims to create vibrant communities where families can thrive. Our residential projects are designed to foster a sense of belonging, with thoughtfully planned spaces that encourage social interaction, security, and overall well-being.",
		image: "/mission-3.svg",
	},
];
---

<Layout title="Mangalya Group - Mission & Vision">
	<Hero title="Mission & Vision" />

	<div class={`container ${styles.mission}`}>
		<div class={styles.card}>
			{
				contentArray.map((item) => {
					return (
						<div class={styles.item}>
							<div class={styles.image}>
								<img
									src={item.image}
									alt={item.heading}
									width="200"
									height="200"
								/>
							</div>

							<div class={styles.info}>
								<h4>{item.heading}</h4>

								<p>{item.text}</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					);
				})
			}
		</div>

		<div class={styles.text}>
			<h3>Future of Mangalya Group in Delhi NCR's Residential Sector</h3>

			<p>
				Mangalya Group envisions playing a pivotal role in shaping the
				residential real estate landscape of Delhi NCR. With a strong
				foundation built on trust, transparency, and quality
				construction, we are committed to delivering homes that meet the
				evolving needs of modern homebuyers. Our projects, including
				Mangalya Ophira and Mangalya Novena Greens, exemplify this
				vision by offering well-planned residential spaces with
				contemporary amenities and thoughtful designs.
			</p>

			<p>
				As the demand for sustainable and affordable housing grows,
				Mangalya Group will continue to integrate eco-friendly
				solutions, innovative architecture, and smart infrastructure
				into its developments. By staying ahead of industry trends and
				maintaining a customer-first approach, we aim to set new
				standards in residential real estate while contributing to the
				broader goal of a Green India.
			</p>

			<p>
				With a strong track record of delivering on promises, Mangalya
				Group remains focused on expanding its presence in Delhi NCR,
				ensuring that every homebuyer finds a place that offers comfort,
				security, and long-term value. Through continuous growth and
				innovation, we look forward to building homes that stand the
				test of time and enhance the quality of urban living.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
